high_descs: Turn around to the sink on the left side.
Pick up the bar of soap from on top of the toilet tank.
Carry the soap and turn to the right, then face the sink on the right side of the counter.
Open the top right drawer and place the soap inside. Shut the drawer.
Look up to the sink and the counter.
Pick up the soap from inside the sink.
Hold the soap and look around.
Open the top right drawer and place the soap inside. Shut the drawer.
anns.task_desc: Place two bars of soap in a drawer.

high_descs: Turn around and face the back of the toilet.
Pick up the bar of soap from the back of the toilet.
Turn and walk to the sink on the right side.
Open the top drawer below the sink on the right side, put the soap in the drawer, close the drawer.
Move closer to the sink in front of you.
Pick up the bar of soap from the sink.
Move further back from the sink.
Open the top drawer on the right, place the soap in the drawer on top of the first bar of soap, close the drawer.
anns.task_desc: To move two bars of soap to the drawer.

high_descs: Turn around and get to the front of the toilet
Grab the soap bar off of the top of the toilet
Turn right and face the drawers at the bottom of the sink
Put the soap in the top right drawer
Move forward and face the sink
Grab the soap bar out of the sink
Back up and face the drawers at the bottom
Put the soap in the top right drawer
anns.task_desc: Putting two bars of soap in a drawer
